live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021200856/http://www.ifc.com/fix/2010/09/will-gluck-easy-a/2 |archive-date=2012-10-21 }}</ref>。拍攝地點早於7月13日成立，主要攝影於2010年7月20日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]的[[曼哈頓中城|曼哈頓中城]]部分開始<ref name="film">{{cite news|last1=Gardner |first1=Elysa |title=Mila Kunis maps out a singular path to stardom |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2011-07-18-mila-kunis-friends-with-benefits_n.htm |accessdate=2015-08-29 |work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |date=2011-07-19 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202724/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/people/2011-07-18-mila-kunis-friends-with-benefits_n.htm |archive-date=2016-03-03 }}</ref>。拍攝於7月—8月初在[[中央公園|中央公園]]和紐約其他地區繼續，隨後遷至[[洛杉磯|加利福尼亞洛杉磯]]<ref name=film/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/friends-benefits-director-gluck-rejoices-coming-home-film-latest-article-1.161052 |title='Friends with Benefits' director Will Gluck rejoices in coming home to film his latest |first=Ethan |last=Sacks |work=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]] |date=2011-07-16 |accessdate=2011-10-22 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505073313/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/friends-benefits-director-gluck-rejoices-coming-home-film-latest-article-1.161052 |archive-date=2015-05-05 }}</ref>。

[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]於導演[[伊万·雷特曼|伊萬·雷特曼]]為他的電影重新命名為《[[飯飯之交|枕邊冇情人]]》後放棄了最初的抗議。後來[[幕寶電影公司|幕寶電影公司]]以《戀搞好朋友》的名稱繼續該項目。同時，[[全國廣播公司|全國廣播公司]]正在開發具同名的情景喜劇，但該電影製作公司表示，由於其製作時間表的關係，他們沒有預期有問題出現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2010/05/21/friends-with-benefits-title-cleared |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100524061135/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2010/05/21/friends-with-benefits-title-cleared/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=2010-05-24 |title=Friends with Benefits Title Cleared |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |last=Sperling |first=Nicole |date=2010-05-21 |accessdate=2010-06-12 }}</ref>。幕寶電影公司選擇加快製作，擔心他們會失去跟派拉蒙影業競逐的電影各稱。電影導演[[威爾·古勒|威爾·古勒]]在談到比較這兩部電影的挫敗感時，他說：「我希望它們之間有更多的空間。現在讓我感到討厭的是，別人說我們正在重製《枕邊冇情人》。我們並沒有把它重製。這兩部電影是同時製作的<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jul/19/entertainment/la-et-will-gluck-20110719 |title=Will Gluck experiences the benefits of success |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |last=Sperling |first=Nicole |date=2011-07-19 |accessdate=2011-07-19 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105212147/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jul/19/entertainment/la-et-will-gluck-20110719 |archive-date=2012-11-05 }}</ref>。」古勒在接受《[[新西蘭先驅報|新西蘭先驅報]]》的採訪時說，這兩部電影是不同的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/movies/news/article.cfm?c_id=200&objectid=10751564|title=Friends With Benefits: Fooling around with romance|work=[[The_New_Zealand_Herald|The New Zealand Herald]]|last=Manelis|first=Michele|date=2011-09-14|accessdate=2011-09-14|archive-date=2018-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001031000/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/movies/news/article.cfm?c_id=200&objectid=10751564|dead-url=no}}</ref>。女主角古妮絲也表達了類似的觀點，她說：「這只是兩部不同的電影。這個世界上...有那麼多故事你可以說。這只是其中之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/movies/articles/2011/07/19/20110719justin-timberlake-mila-kunis-comedy-has-benefits.html|title=Q&A: Justin Timberlake, Mila Kunis: Comedy has 'Benefits'|work=[[The_Arizona_Republic|The Arizona Republic]]|last=Goodykoontz|first=Bill|date=2011-07-19|accessdate=2011-07-30|archive-date=2012-08-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69zuDM3Jm?url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/movies/articles/2011/07/19/20110719justin-timberlake-mila-kunis-comedy-has-benefits.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」

電影的首支預告片於2011年3月16日發行<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reynolds |first1=Simon |title=World Exclusive: 'Friends With Benefits' trailer |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/at-the-movies/a309364/world-exclusive-friends-with-benefits-trailer.html |publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |accessdate=2015-08-29 |date=2011-03-16 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924063002/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/at-the-movies/a309364/world-exclusive-friends-with-benefits-trailer.html |archive-date=2015-09-24 }}</ref>。該預告片隨後在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上發布，並在48小時內吸引了超過100萬的瀏覽次數，成為當天觀看次數最多影片的第二位，以及在電影類別中觀看次數最多的視頻<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/friends-with-benefits-preview-gets-over-a-million-views-in-48-hours-viral-video-spotlight-2270698.html |title='Friends with Benefits' preview gets over a million views in 48 hours: viral video spotlight |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=2011-04-20 |accessdate=2011-04-20 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711142711/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/friends-with-benefits-preview-gets-over-a-million-views-in-48-hours-viral-video-spotlight-2270698.html |archive-date=2011-07-11 }}</ref>。隨後，對於《戀搞好朋友》的促銷活動有所增加，包括來自[[Facebook|Facebook]]和[[Twitter|Twitter]]的促銷視頻。添布力與古妮絲也登上《[[ELLE|ELLE]]》雜誌的封面以支持電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/07/06/mila-kunis-and-justin-tim_n_891305.html |title=Mila Kunis And Justin Timberlake Debut 'Friends With Benefits' PSA |date=2011-07-06 |accessdate=2011-07-07 |work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110709175009/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/07/06/mila-kunis-and-justin-tim_n_891305.html |archive-date=2011-07-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/g2596/lust-in-translation-justin-timberlake-mila-kunis-567648/ |title=Lust In Translation: Justin Timberlake and Mila Kunis |date=2011-07-07 |accessdate=2011-07-07 |work=[[Elle_(magazine)|Elle]] |first=Millea |last=Holly |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112235033/http://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/g2596/lust-in-translation-justin-timberlake-mila-kunis-567648/ |archive-date=2015-01-12 }}</ref>。

=== 創作 ===
導演威爾·古勒表示，故事的概念始於他想跟古妮絲和添布力合作的想法，並解釋說他為兩位演員重新寫了劇本。隨著這些變化，古勒表示想吸引更多成年觀眾，並且他「也想製作更多關於性愛以及關係的成人電影」<ref name="Yamato, Jen">{{cite web |url=http://news.moviefone.com/2010/09/18/easy-a-will-gluck-interview |title=Easy A Director Will Gluck on Teen Sex and '80s Fantasy Boyfriends |publisher=[[Moviefone|Moviefone]] |first=Yamato |last=Jen |date=2010-09-18 |accessdate=2010-09-18 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130716183112/http://news.moviefone.com/2010/09/18/easy-a-will-gluck-interview |archive-date=2013-07-16 }}</ref>。他接著把《戀搞好朋友》的故事情節與[[凯瑟琳·赫本|嘉芙蓮·協賓]]與[[史賓塞·屈賽|史賓沙·德利西]]之間的關係進行了比較<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hassan |first1=Genevieve |title=Friends With Benefits: a new generation of rom–com |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-14787785 |accessdate=2015-08-30 |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2011-09-09 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924045135/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-14787785 |archive-date=2015-09-24 }}</ref>。

{{quote box|width=25em|align=right|quote=作為觀眾，我不想走進一部名為《戀搞好朋友》的電影並看到PG-13的版本。對於我來說，如果沒有擁有這樣的電影名稱，你就沒有這樣的電影。|source=—[[賈斯汀·提姆布萊克|賈斯汀·添布力]]<ref name=latimes/>}}

在接受《{{le|電影在線|Movieline}}》的訪問時，古勒進一步討論了電影的情節，稱《戀搞好朋友》將會在很大程度上跟年輕一代有關。他補充說：「他們在整部電影中對這些浪漫喜劇進行評論，並且在經歷故事情節時，他們意識到自己正處於浪漫喜劇故事中—就作為兩個不在電影中的普通人會對此發表評論。他們非常清楚自己在這個故事中……但他們最終擁抱著正在經歷浪漫喜劇時刻的事實<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movieline.com/2010/08/19/will-gluck-interview-easy-a/ |title=Easy A Director Will Gluck |publisher=[[Movieline|Movieline]] |first=Buchanan |last=Kyle |date=2010-08-19 |accessdate=2010-08-22 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902232642/http://movieline.com/2010/08/19/will-gluck-interview-easy-a/ |archive-date=2012-09-02 }}</ref>。」添布力在接受《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的訪問時解釋說，他跟古勒擔任著《戀搞好朋友》的幽默和基調的作者<ref name=latimes>{{cite web|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/12/justin-timberlake.html |title=Justin Timberlake: I'm obviously not the best actor in the world |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |last=Lee |first=Chris |date=2010-12-09 |accessdate=2010-12-10 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213031202/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/12/justin-timberlake.html |archive-date=2010-12-13 }}</ref>。電影投入製作前，添布力與古妮絲為劇本進行了一個多月的製作。導演古勒帶同20頁劇本跟演員們見面，而三人會擊敗劇本，改變對白並捍衛著每個角色的視角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/07/justin-timberlake-on-friends-with-benefits-director-will-gluck-we-will-make-plenty-of-movies-togethe.html |title=Justin Timberlake sees more Will Gluck in his future |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |last=Sperling |first=Nicole |date=2011-07-25 |accessdate=2011-07-25 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120716022526/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2011/07/justin-timberlake-on-friends-with-benefits-director-will-gluck-we-will-make-plenty-of-movies-togethe.html |archive-date=2012-07-16 }}</ref>。

