《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的{{le|曼諾拉·達吉斯|Manohla Dargis}}稱讚《戀搞好朋友》的「輕快、迅速和有趣的喜劇」，並稱讚了男女主角之間的化學作用<ref name="nytimes">{{cite web|url=https://movies.nytimes.com/2011/07/22/movies/justin-timberlake-in-friends-with-benefits-review.html |title=It's Just Sex. We're Just Friends. You Know the Rules. Etc., Etc. |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |last=Dargis |first=Manohla |authorlink=Manohla Dargis |date=2011-07-22 |accessdate=2011-07-22 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723220044/http://movies.nytimes.com/2011/07/22/movies/justin-timberlake-in-friends-with-benefits-review.html |archive-date=2011-07-23 }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的[[罗杰·伊伯特|羅渣·伊拔]]給這部電影三顆星，並評論了這部電影：「然而，並不是每個浪漫喜劇都擁有很好的對話，並且很快就能完成。」他補充說：「古妮絲在開場時以自己的方式快速講話，就好像她在引用《[[Juno少女孕記|Juno少女孕記]]》一樣，而添布力很容易就跟上。在某些基本層面來說，我只是喜歡看他們<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/friends-with-benefits-2011 |title=Friends with Benefits |work=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]] |first=Ebert |last=Roger |date=2011-07-20 |accessdate=2011-07-22 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602095138/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/friends-with-benefits-2011 |archive-date=2013-06-02 }}</ref>。」《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的彼得·德布魯格（Peter Debruge）發現該情節是可預測的和良性的；然而，他讚賞劇組，稱古妮絲為「自然的喜劇演員」，而添布力則「散發出[[威爾·史密斯|韋·史密夫]]為首的那種星光」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2011/film/reviews/friends-with-benefits-1117945660/ |title=Friends with Benefits |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |first=Debruge |last=Peter |date=2011-07-18 |accessdate=2011-07-22 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130726025647/http://variety.com/2011/film/reviews/friends-with-benefits-1117945660/ |archive-date=2013-07-26 }}</ref>。同樣，{{le|沙龍網站|Salon (website)}}的安德魯·奧赫希爾（Andrew O'Hehir）斷言，儘管這部電影的結論令人失望，但儘管如此這仍然是「夏季分流的獎勵」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.salon.com/2011/07/22/friends_with_benefits_3/  |title="Friends With Benefits": Justin and Mila in the other, other sex–pals movie  |first=Andrew  |last=O'Hehir  |work=[[Salon_(website)|Salon]]  |date=2011-07-21  |accessdate=2011-10-22  |url-status=live  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111018160638/http://www.salon.com/2011/07/22/friends_with_benefits_3/  |archive-date=2011-10-18  }}</ref>。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的作者{{le|彼得·布拉德肖|Peter Bradshaw}}對這部電影反應負面，表示「觀看它並無好處」。布拉德肖給這部電影評為1／5顆星<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/sep/08/friends-with-benefits-review |title=Friends With Benefits – review |first=Peter |last=Bradshaw |work=The Guardian |date=2011-09-08 |accessdate=2011-10-22 |url-status=live |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151119195757/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/sep/08/friends-with-benefits-review |archive-date= 2015-11-19 }}</ref>。

